      "index": 3,
      "title": "Shoulder Press (Machine Plates)",
      "notes": "Sets: 3 Working Sets.\n\nTarget: 8-12 reps @ RPE 10.\n\nRest: 3m 0s\n\nBase weight: 5.4kg\n\nSequencing: Executed here while triceps are still relatively fresh to maximize mechanical load.\n\nGrip: Vertical handles. Neutral grip.\n\nPillar: Squeeze glutes. \"Double Chin\" position. Prevent lower back arching.\n\nRange: Drive the weight up, but stop just short of elbow lockout to protect the heavily taxed triceps. Drop back down to ear-level.",
