    {
      "index": 4,
      "title": "Incline Chest Press (Machine)",
      "notes": "Incline Chest Press (Machine) | Magnum Incline Bench Press\n\nSets: 3 Working Sets.\n\nTarget: 6-10 reps @ RPE 10.\n\nRest: 3m 0s (Increased from 2m 0s for heavy compound ATP replenishment).\n\nTempo: 3-second eccentric drop deep into the stretch.\n\nBase weight: 5.4kg\n\nThe Tricep Bypass: Push explosively out of the bottom, but do not lock your elbows. Stop the movement while there is still a 15-degree bend in the arm, then immediately begin the 3-second lowering phase. Keep the tension trapped in the pectoral muscle.",
